Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.51,0:00:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.47,0:00:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.39,0:00:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.27,0:00:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before his death
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.24,0:00:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drove people around the world to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.00,0:00:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure? If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.76,0:00:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.97,0:00:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men rushed onto the\NGrand Line in pursuit of romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.62,0:00:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly entered a Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.52,0:00:35.09,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We’re going to gather up all our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.11,0:00:40.93,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search of something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.95,0:00:47.06,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,ONE PIECE!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.08,0:00:52.75,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Compasses only cause delays
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.77,0:00:58.44,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Delirious with fever, I take the helm
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.46,0:01:06.46,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If the dusty treasure map has\Nbeen verified, it’s not a legend!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.72,0:01:16.41,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to personal storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.43,0:01:21.53,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,simply ride aboard someone else’s biorhythm
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.55,0:01:25.34,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and pretend it isn’t there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.36,0:01:30.81,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We’re going to gather up all our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.83,0:01:36.31,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search of something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.33,0:01:42.57,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,A coin in my pocket,\Nand you wanna be my friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.59,0:01:48.25,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We are, We are on the cruise!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.27,0:01:52.86,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We are!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.88,0:01:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.08,0:01:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.80,0:02:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.79,0:02:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before his death
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.25,0:02:09.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drove people around the world to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.28,0:02:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure? If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.44,0:02:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.36,0:02:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men rushed onto the\NGrand Line in pursuit of romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.41,0:02:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly entered a Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.39,0:02:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.39,0:02:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for being bullheaded!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.31,0:02:45.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.50,0:02:48.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.70,0:02:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot! Grab my hand already!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.76,0:03:05.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Wanted Posters Make It Around the World!\NCelebration in Their Hometowns
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.71,0:03:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as the Ship Moves Forward!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.30,0:03:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meteor... Fist!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.59,0:03:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Luffy-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.43,0:03:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vice Admiral Garp sure doesn't show\Nany mercy, even to his own grandson.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.46,0:03:43.18,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Navy"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.20,0:03:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, our town's heroes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.83,0:03:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be taken out by the Navy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.38,0:03:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, rooting for them could get us in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.72,0:03:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Straw Hats!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.68,0:03:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run, run, then keep running!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.49,0:04:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.44,0:04:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.87,0:04:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the heck? They're furling the sails?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.66,0:04:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if they gave up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.92,0:04:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give up?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.22,0:04:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt Luffy's given up,\Nbut then, just what is he up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.67,0:04:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up! Furl the sails!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.55,0:04:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Furl the sails!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.13,0:04:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Are you really sure about this, Franky?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.48,0:04:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Are you asking me if I'm really sure?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.89,0:04:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You dummy! Have faith in this ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.75,0:04:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's right! Have faith in it, you dummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.10,0:04:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You jerk! You dummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.86,0:04:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp, just a minute ago, you were...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.02,0:04:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess it doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.22,0:04:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a hand, you bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.20,0:04:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, what the hell are they\Nthinking at a damn busy time like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.12,0:05:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Franky, I've furled the sails, as you said to.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.11,0:05:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'd better hurry up, or the\Nbattleship will catch up with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.00,0:05:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not quite yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.06,0:05:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.86,0:05:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We still haven't named this ship yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.17,0:05:13.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Name?! At a time like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.29,0:05:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. You don't wanna depart\Nin an unnamed ship, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.18,0:05:22.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.15,0:05:24.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, a name like "Something-or-other Lion"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.10,0:05:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! I got a name that sounds strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.34,0:05:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The "Bear! Polar Bear! Lion!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.72,0:05:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one would give a ship\Na weird name like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.31,0:05:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, the "Tiger! Wolf! Lion!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.27,0:05:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop just listing animal names like that!\NWhat is it, some sort of a curse?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.17,0:05:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Squid! Octopus! Chimpanzee!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.58,0:05:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you're not even putting "lion" in it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.78,0:05:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, "lion" is on the right track.\NBut the Galley-La guys were like...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.66,0:05:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This figurehead looks good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.66,0:05:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's a nice sunflower!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.96,0:05:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a sunflower, you idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.46,0:05:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's just natural that\Nyou guys wouldn't get it right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.90,0:06:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this is a ship that the future\NKing of the Pirates will board.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.48,0:06:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you made it with that\Nhope in mind, right, Franky?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.07,0:06:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. He'll set sail into\Na sea filled with savage beasts
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.40,0:06:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and rise to the top. So I wanted\Na figurehead suitable for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.07,0:06:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a splendid sun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.44,0:06:11.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a sun, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.94,0:06:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A ship that'll cross a thousand rigorous\Noceans cheerfully, just like the sun...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.06,0:06:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's perfect for them!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.62,0:06:23.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said it's not a sun, you Stupid-berg!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.37,0:06:27.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think about this\Nfor the ship's name, Franky?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.01,0:06:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The pirate ship...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.93,0:06:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Thousand Sunny!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.22,0:06:41.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.35,0:06:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.08,0:06:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's better than the "Dumpling!\NGorilla! Lion!" name I came up with!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.00,0:06:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this, a word game?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.67,0:06:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds better than\N"Boss Lionel" that crossed my mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.72,0:06:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Better than the "Darkness" that I thought of...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.25,0:06:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Better than the "Monsieur\NSunflower" that I thought of...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.16,0:06:59.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you guys lost your marbles?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.83,0:07:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A ship that crosses a thousand oceans...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.83,0:07:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How lovely! And so is the sun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.08,0:07:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, you guys! That was\Njust to start things off.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.46,0:07:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one I came up with sounds a lot better!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.89,0:07:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's my name for the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.05,0:07:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--The "New Battle Franky,\NLion Gang Champion"!\N--Let's use what Ice pops came up with! I like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.72,0:07:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--"Lion Gang Champion"!\N--"Thousand Sunny," huh? That's a good name!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.89,0:07:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I agree!\N--Let's get along, Sunny!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.18,0:07:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess deciding on the ship's name has\Nhelped us brace ourselves for departure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.97,0:07:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.56,0:07:30.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Franky, what're you\Nbooing about over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.90,0:07:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and shake them off with\Nthe secret weapon or whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.96,0:07:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you'd better hurry up.\NThe battleship is already nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.45,0:07:39.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, fine, stop bugging me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.25,0:07:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a last look at this beautiful\Ncity of water while you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.19,0:07:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In just a second, this island\Nis going to be out of sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.47,0:07:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.65,0:07:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.84,0:08:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Coby and...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.64,0:08:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was glad I got to see you\Nafter such a long time!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.91,0:08:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Call my name, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.23,0:08:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What, Luffy? I've got more cannonballs left!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.78,0:08:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meteor... Fist!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.94,0:08:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.13,0:08:30.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna run with all our might now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.38,0:08:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll see you guys again someday!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.67,0:08:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-san's cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.79,0:08:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you talk cheeky?!\NYou're nothing but my kid's kid! Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.18,0:08:42.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vice Admiral Garp, please calm down a little!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.47,0:08:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ice pops! We decided to use the\Nname you came up with for the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.89,0:08:49.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the nice name!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.11,0:08:54.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone! Thanks for everything!\NWe're taking off!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.63,0:08:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds like he's saying something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.24,0:09:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't even make it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.40,0:09:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like pirates can't even\Ndepart without making a racket.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.93,0:09:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.36,0:09:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is an astonishing emergency\Naccelerator made with a huge air cannon
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.18,0:09:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,taking advantage of the strength\Nof the treasure tree Adam!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.46,0:09:19.51,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,2000)}"Navy"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.53,0:09:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-A massive iron ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.76,0:09:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.31,0:09:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.31,0:09:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahhh! We're gonna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.48,0:09:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way we'll survive that! That's not possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.59,0:09:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you underestimate me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.48,0:09:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Run, Luffy-san! You're gonna get killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.50,0:09:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Franky! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.04,0:09:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you'll get hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.70,0:10:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.30,0:10:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coup de Burst!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.01,0:10:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ship... flew... away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.57,0:10:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.71,0:10:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.98,0:10:50.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember experiencing this feeling before.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.50,0:10:52.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Merry...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.06,0:10:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It consumes three barrels of cola,\Nbut it lets us fly one kilometer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.56,0:11:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing the Going Merry\Ncould do that this ship can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.50,0:11:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It exceeds the Merry in every way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.51,0:11:09.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the Merry's brave soul will be\Ninherited by the Thousand Sunny.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.16,0:11:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it breaks down, I'll fix it perfectly!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.31,0:11:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to the ship and weapons,\Nrely on me for anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.12,0:11:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From today on, this is your ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.83,0:11:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.64,0:11:31.90,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Navy"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.92,0:11:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They sure showed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.66,0:11:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They escaped.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.96,0:11:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my grandson!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.33,0:11:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, he didn't come with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.18,0:12:02.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course he wouldn't.\NBut the king of snipers promised us
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.74,0:12:04.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that he'd come to Elbaf\Nsome day with his friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.75,0:12:05.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll look forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.83,0:12:10.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll wait patiently.\NA giant's life span is 300 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.59,0:12:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We did some good work!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.32,0:12:15.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Now, let's go back\Nto our work place, shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.43,0:12:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or do we wanna go get a drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.29,0:12:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I'm in!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.80,0:12:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're heading back to\Nthe station, Chimney, Gonbe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.03,0:12:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see... How did Bro do things?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.92,0:12:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beats me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.58,0:12:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were just doing whatever\Nhe told us to do, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.24,0:12:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna starve to death like this, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.91,0:12:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Iceberg!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.78,0:12:41.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... I knew this would happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.35,0:12:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?! What'd you come here for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.32,0:12:46.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're worried about work,\NI can give you some.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.29,0:12:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to Galley-La's headquarters\None by one, one per day, every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.03,0:12:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Are you sure, Iceber... I mean, Bro?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.80,0:12:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,New Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.79,0:13:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't call me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.53,0:13:16.80,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1)}"An island in the Grand Line"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.82,0:13:17.79,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Commodore Smoker!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.81,0:13:18.89,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for your help, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.91,0:13:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? The bounty on that pirate\NI just caught is 50 million?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.21,0:13:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.41,0:13:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How ridiculous! What kind of\Ncriteria does the Navy use?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.83,0:13:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, the days sure are boring...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.92,0:13:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smoker-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.21,0:13:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ensign Tashigi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.51,0:13:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you seen the wanted posters?\NThe Straw Hats are...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.63,0:13:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you talking to?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.21,0:13:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.22,0:13:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! I-I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.03,0:13:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wear your glasses, you idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.92,0:13:48.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're marines after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.00,0:13:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since the Navy is hierarchical in nature,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.06,0:13:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there's a limit to my freedom\Nso long as I'm only a captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.99,0:13:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What we need now is higher ranks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.02,0:13:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After the incident in Enies Lobby,\Npirates all around the world
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.78,0:14:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,started acknowledging that\Nthe Straw Hats have the edge.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.40,0:14:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.26,0:14:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On my pride, I'm gonna crush\Nthem in the New World!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.46,0:14:18.09,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1)}"Sea Restaurant 'Baratie,'\NEast Blue"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.11,0:14:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The judicial island Enies Lobby is the front door
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.72,0:14:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that leads to the World Government,\Na huge organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.47,0:14:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that they've caused it to fall,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.12,0:14:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,neither the Navy nor pirates\Nwill leave them alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.08,0:14:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can say that the Straw Hats\Nare now known all around the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.51,0:14:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so is this wanted poster.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.81,0:14:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji! You're the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.18,0:14:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this incredible?!\NIt's the spitting image of him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.58,0:14:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Foot Sanji with a\N77-million bounty used to work here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.45,0:14:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We hope you'll come visit us again\Nhere at the sea restaurant Baratie!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.67,0:14:55.98,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1)}"'Fusha Village' (Luffy's hometown),\NEast Blue"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.00,0:14:59.32,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Party time! Let's have a party today!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.34,0:15:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the most successful one in the\NEast Blue with a 300-million bounty!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.37,0:15:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers to our Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.48,0:15:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, you idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.08,0:15:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shame on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.00,0:15:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.62,0:15:18.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.97,0:15:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously... No one's listening to me,\Nthe mayor of the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.50,0:15:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy seems like he's having a fun life.\NHe's got such a cute pet, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.72,0:15:30.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So these kids are his friends, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.67,0:15:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Friends"? They don't look friendly to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.62,0:15:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone from our village\Nbecame a vicious criminal
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.13,0:15:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that made the entire world his enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.18,0:15:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never heard of pirates picking\Na fight with the World Government!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.12,0:15:45.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.85,0:15:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To start with, what is Garp doing,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.09,0:15:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,allowing his own grandson to run\Nfree and commit such a crime?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.11,0:15:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something's wrong with that whole family.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.25,0:15:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does Dadan know about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.07,0:15:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.06,0:15:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.57,0:16:04.36,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1)}"'Syrup Village' (Usopp's hometown),\NEast Blue"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.38,0:16:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,King of snipers... Yes!\NThere's no mistake about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.51,0:16:09.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Usopp-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.78,0:16:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Right?\N--This nose has to be our captain's!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.46,0:16:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.38,0:16:15.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People at the village wouldn't believe us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.70,0:16:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, his bounty is 30 million, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.45,0:16:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we thought you'd agree, Kaya-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.59,0:16:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They don't know how incredible our captain is!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.31,0:16:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our captain turns all lies into truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.12,0:16:29.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This mask looks cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.15,0:16:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's make it using clay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.64,0:16:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Where are you going, Kaya-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.95,0:16:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go home and continue\Nstudying to become a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.54,0:16:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd better hurry up and\Nbecome a full-fledged doctor
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.78,0:16:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so that I can treat Usopp-san if\Nhe's injured when he comes back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.23,0:16:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I envy Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.02,0:16:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hit him if he makes Kaya-san unhappy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.51,0:16:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.79,0:16:53.22,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1)}"'Shimotsuki Village' (Zoro's hometown),\NEast Blue"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.24,0:16:54.32,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei! Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.34,0:16:55.95,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it true that the Pirate Hunter Zoro
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.97,0:16:57.23,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,used to train at this dojo?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.25,0:16:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.23,0:17:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you kids shouldn't look up to him, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.22,0:17:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.61,0:17:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? He's so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.34,0:17:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Teach us how to become pirates, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.72,0:17:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't teach him how to become a pirate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.64,0:17:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you telling the truth?\NDon't play favorites, Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.61,0:17:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Good grief, what a troublesome alumnus.\N--He's amazing! I wanna\Nbe a swordsman like him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.40,0:17:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sure was surprised to hear about\Nthe incident on the judicial island,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.39,0:17:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but Zoro-kun, I think there's\Nno doubt in your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.70,0:17:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter who you become,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.64,0:17:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if you're faithful to your swordsmanship,\Nthat's all that matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.99,0:17:29.57,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1)}"'Cocoyashi Village' (Nami's hometown),\NEast Blue"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.59,0:17:31.39,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Gen-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.41,0:17:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, I brought some tangerines.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.24,0:17:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What, you brought them again, Nojiko?\NI told you I'd buy them at the store.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.29,0:17:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, just take them.\NDon't act like we're strangers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.08,0:17:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think of you like a father to Nami and I, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.65,0:17:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was never consulted.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.31,0:17:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.43,0:17:48.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? Oh, this...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.93,0:17:54.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been calling the Navy Headquarters\Nto complain, but I can't get through at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.86,0:17:55.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Complain?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.91,0:17:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.39,0:18:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They can't just release a lewd wanted\Nposter like this to the entire world!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.55,0:18:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She'll have more suitors after her\Nthan bounty hunters! Outrageous!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.37,0:18:10.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you like that picture itself, right?\NYou did blow it up quite a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.79,0:18:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let it go, because this\Nproves that they're keeping...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.21,0:18:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you guys ever do anything\Nto take away Nami's smile...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.34,0:18:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I will come kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.42,0:18:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the promise they made you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.43,0:18:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, it's true, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.51,0:18:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that's those pirates' business, not mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.58,0:18:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, would you have preferred\Nif she looked rough in the picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.54,0:18:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! That'd be outrageous!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.10,0:18:41.10,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1)}"'Sakura Kingdom' (Chopper's hometown),\NGrand Line"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.97,0:18:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Kureha.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.59,0:18:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you have me come here for, Dalton?\NI'm pretty busy, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.22,0:18:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm sorry, but I definitely\Nwanted to show these to you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.78,0:19:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it? You wanna know\Nmy secret to staying young?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.70,0:19:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To start with, Dalton, why don't you live\Nin the castle like kings normally do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.24,0:19:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can let you use some of the rooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.85,0:19:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I like living in this familiar village.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.96,0:19:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, I like rice cooked with chestnuts.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.12,0:19:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? These are those Straw Hat lads.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.23,0:19:24.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These wanted posters were issued\Nafter the big incident the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.04,0:19:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.24,0:19:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think his bounty amount\Nis some sort of a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.73,0:19:32.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care as long as I can see his face.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.17,0:19:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... This is wonderful news.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.75,0:19:40.82,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1)}"The sand kingdom 'Alabasta,'\NGrand Line"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.84,0:19:43.20,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.22,0:19:48.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nico Robin... Why is Miss All Sunday\Na member of Luffy-kun's gang?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.34,0:19:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She surely was a mysterious woman,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.75,0:19:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so much so that something about\Nher stuck in my mind, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.85,0:19:57.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Vivi-sama finds this out,\Nshe'll probably feel very sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.45,0:20:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that. I already know,\Nbut it doesn't bother me at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.73,0:20:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It doesn't bother you at all? I thought\Nyou'd be more shocked than anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.97,0:20:10.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you stayed close to Luffy-san,\Nyou wouldn't understand what he's thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.53,0:20:16.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a waste of time thinking about it,\Nbut you can trust everything they do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.14,0:20:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the man who'll be King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.92,0:20:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's of quite a different caliber.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.91,0:20:27.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How magnanimous! You've grown, Vivi-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.84,0:20:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, why are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.97,0:20:32.80,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1)}"Land of white soil 'Baltigo,'\NGrand Line"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.82,0:20:36.83,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,The rebel group took Centaurea in the South Blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.85,0:20:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Another country has fallen...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.61,0:20:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We did it! Now the North Blue's--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.46,0:20:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is no cause for rejoicing. This is a war.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.23,0:20:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, sir, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.41,0:20:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.30,0:20:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's Straw Hat Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.88,0:20:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the guy who actually\Ndefeated Crocodile in Alabasta.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.24,0:21:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After the incident in Enies Lobby,\Nhis pirate group is becoming so big
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.80,0:21:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that the government can no\Nlonger hide their existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.07,0:21:10.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The total bounty for the entire group\Nis 667 million and 50 Berries.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.59,0:21:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that their captain is the\Ngrandson of Garp from the Na...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.53,0:21:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.19,0:21:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to get some air.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.18,0:21:24.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Live as you please, Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.61,0:21:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the flow of time, as a result of\Nvarious circumstances and strong spirits...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.49,0:21:32.21,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1)}"'The World's Most Heinous Criminal'\NRevolutionist Dragon (Monkey D. Dragon)"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.23,0:21:34.65,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,...people come to question the world they live in!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.67,0:21:42.67,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,The day we meet will come at some point.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.48,0:21:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.71,0:21:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.72,0:21:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.27,0:21:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, once again...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.68,0:21:57.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To Robin and Usopp, who came back to us,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.05,0:22:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to our new friend, Franky...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.27,0:22:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and to our pirate ship, the Thousand Sunny!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.46,0:22:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Cheers!\N--Cheers!
